Privacy Policy - Handboard Training
**Privacy Policy for Hangboard Training App**
Last Updated: Jan 1st, 2025
**Introduction**
Welcome to Hangboard Training, a mobile fitness app developed and published by KikkoApps Pte. Ltd. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.
**Information We Collect**
**Personal Information:**
– We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and profile image URL to manage your user account.
**Fitness Data:**
– The app may collect and store data related to your hangboard training activities, such as workout duration, exercise routines, and performance metrics.
**Device Information:**
– We do not collect device information, including but not limited to your device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers. However when the app displays Ads, ads providers may collect some of this information.
**Usage Data:**
– We do not collect information about your use of the app, including the features you use, the content you access, besides all cases listed in #2 and #3 of this policy document.
**How We Use Your Information**
**Personalization:**
– We don’t use your personal information to personalize your app experience, providing tailored content and recommendations.However when the app displays Ads, ads providers may use this information to target ads.
**Improvements and Updates:**
– Your data helps us analyze app usage patterns, identify areas for improvement, and deliver updates to enhance your experience.
**Communication:**
– We may use your email address to send you important updates, notifications, and newsletters related to the app.
**Legal Compliance:**
– We may use and disclose your information as required by law or in response to legal processes.
**Data Security**
We take appropriate measures to secure your personal information and protect it from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
**Third-Party Services**
Hangboard Training may integrate third-party services for analytics, advertising, and other purposes. These services may have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them.
**Children’s Privacy**
Hangboard Training is not intended for users under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will take steps to delete such information.
**Changes to this Privacy Policy**
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. You will be notified of any significant changes via the app or email.
**Contact Us**
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [support@kikkoapps.com].
Thank you for using Hangboard Training!
